verbose_text: It was observed that the downregulation of AMFR induced cell cycle arrest and increased the apoptosis of the THP-1 cells, In addition, the expression levels of ROCK2, cyclin D1 and B-cell lymphoma (Bcl) -2 were reduced by downregulation of AMFR and enhanced by overexpression of AMFR-C.
evidence: cell cycle arrest and increased the apoptosis
